    "## SECTION 13 — Evaluation Metrics\n",
    "\n",
    "**Classification:** accuracy + confusion matrix  \n",
    "**Regression:** MSE + MAE (following the `mae_loss_wgtd` and `do_eval` patterns from `train_utils.py`)"
